name: ETH Snek
description: Introducing ETH Snek ($SNEK) – the ultimate meme token of 2025, celebrating the Year of the Snake with a slithering twist! More than just a snake-themed memecoin, $SNEK aims to dominate the meme token landscape with its innovative approach and strong community backing. With its clever branding and commitment to becoming a cultural icon, $SNEK is not just riding the wave of the Chinese Zodiac but redefining what it means to be a top-tier memecoin. It is completely community-driven, with 0% tax, liquidity burned, and ownership renounced to ensure transparency and trust within the ecosystem. Get ready to embrace the year of $SNEK – where memes, innovation, and community come together to strike big!
